OL,3,C82-year-old man stabbed and tied up in
OL,4,Cburglary
OL,6,FDetectives are calling for people to
OL,7,Fkeep their doors and windows locked
OL,8,Fafter a series of burglaries which
OL,9,Fresulted in one man in his 80s being
OL,10,Fstabbed and locked in his cupboard.
OL,12,FThe 82-year-old victim was struck with
OL,13,Fhis own walking stick after he
OL,14,Fdiscovered a man hiding under a dining
OL,15,Ftable in his home on Mellaieu Street
OL,16,Fin Royton, Oldham on Sunday 15
OL,17,FFebruary.
