OL,6,FThe offender then tied the victim's
OL,7,Fhands and ankles with a cable before
OL,8,Fstabbing him and locking him in a
OL,9,Fcupboard.
OL,11,FThe offender stole the victim's wallet
OL,12,Fand demanded the PIN for his bank
OL,13,Fcard, which was later used around
OL,14,Fmidnight on Oldham Road.
OL,16,FDespite his injuries, the victim
OL,17,Fmanaged to free himself and call his
OL,18,Fdaughter for help. He is now receiving
OL,19,Ftreatment at the Royal Oldham Hospital.
