OL,6,FPolice are now searching for the
OL,7,Foffender, who was described as a black
OL,8,Fmale wearing a covid-style face mask
OL,9,Fand gloves.
OL,11,FA similar description was given after
OL,12,Fan earlier burglary on Monday 10
OL,13,FFebruary, leading police to believe an
OL,14,Findividual may be targeting elderly
OL,15,Fpeople in Royton.
