OL,3,C82-year-old man stabbed and tied up in
OL,4,Cburglary
OL,6,FIn the earlier incident, a "black male
OL,7,Fof large build, approximately 6ft
OL,8,Ftall, with big curly hair" held two
OL,9,Felderly victims at knife point in
OL,10,Ftheir homes. He stole both of their
OL,11,Fwallets and their phones, before
OL,12,Ftrying to force them to drink an
OL,13,F"unknown liquid".
OL,15,FIn both cases, there was no sign of
OL,16,Fforced entry. Instead, it is believed
OL,17,Fthe offender gained access through
OL,18,Ffront doors that had been closed but
OL,19,Fleft unlocked.
