OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Zahid Latif
OL,7,Ffrom Oldham CID said: "We are taking
OL,8,Fthis extremely seriously.
OL,10,F"Neighbourhood officers are carrying
OL,11,Fout increased patrols in the area, and
OL,12,FOldham Council and Adult Social Care
OL,13,Fhave been fully briefed.
OL,15,F"Our enquiries are well underway to
OL,16,Flocate and identify the man
OL,17,Fresponsible for intimidating and
OL,18,Fcommitting these horrific crimes
OL,19,Fagainst vulnerable members of our
OL,20,Fcommunity.
