OL,6,F"GMP will not tolerate this behaviour.
OL,7,FDetectives will be relentless in their
OL,8,Fsearch for this offender, and we will
OL,9,Fuse every resource available to bring
OL,10,Fhim into custody. We are here to keep
OL,11,Fpeople safe, and that is exactly what
OL,12,Fwe intend to do.
OL,14,F"I want to remind everyone to ensure
OL,15,Ftheir windows and doors are locked,
OL,16,Feven when at home, and to support
OL,17,Felderly neighbours or relatives who
OL,18,Fmay feel unsettled at this time."
